metadata.name: Parallela T-Shirt (IRL unclaimed)
metadata.description:
Tokens are eligible to claim physical products, but ALWAYS check the tokenâ€™s live metadata for physical claim status [here](https://dgrealta.unxd.com/claim-status) before purchase.

The claim status may be outdated on OpenSea and the status can change if the original owner claims the physical while your OpenSea purchase completes.

Physical claim period runs from October 1, 2022 at 12pm GMT until October 18, 2022 at 11:59PM GMT. Physical claim MUST occur during this window in order to be accepted. Free shipping to 100 countries.

The Parallela T-shirt is 100% made in Italy. Coming in 4 styles to select from, this T-shirt has a splash of color and comfort. This token entitles the owner to claim 1 of 4 physical T-shirt styles during the claim period, only on UNXD.com. It also entitles the owner to a future digital wearable.

The physical T-shirts are not available anywhere else, are personally designed by Domenico Dolce and Stefano Gabbana, and are 100% made in Italy.

After claim, this NFT will convert to the digital version matching the physical claimed.

Join [Discord](https://discord.gg/unxd) for more information.
